column16: Martin Prado grounds out, shortstop Pete Kozma to first baseman Allen Craig.

Didi Gregorius walks.   Gerardo Parra to 2nd.
Gerardo Parra bunt pops into a force out, third baseman David Freese to shortstop Pete Kozma.   Cody Ross out at 2nd.    Gerardo Parra to 1st.
Joaquin Arias grounds into a double play, shortstop Pete Kozma to second baseman Matt Carpenter to first baseman Matt Adams.   Hunter Pence out at 2nd.
Hunter Pence singles on a line drive to left fielder Matt Holliday.   Buster Posey to 2nd.
Buster Posey singles on a ground ball to center fielder Jon Jay.
Buster Posey grounds out, shortstop Pete Kozma to first baseman Matt Adams.
Hunter Pence grounds out, third baseman Matt Carpenter to first baseman Matt Adams.
Joaquin Arias flies out to center fielder Jon Jay.
Victor Marte intentionally walks Chris Getz.
Eric Hosmer doubles (8) on a ground ball to right fielder Carlos Beltran.   Alex Gordon scores.    Alcides Escobar scores.    David Lough to 3rd.

Alcides Escobar hit by pitch.    Alex Gordon to 2nd.
